en.description:
THE FIRST TAKE is a YouTube Channel dedicated to filming musicians and singers performing in a single take.

Episode 521 marks the first appearance of CRYCHIC from BanG Dream!, a mix media project spanning TV anime, games, comics, and live performances showcasing voice actors on stage. The 5-piece band who reunited in the latest episode of the anime series will perform â€œHaruhikage,â€ a track featured in the 2023 TV anime BanG Dream! Itâ€™s MyGO!!!!!, that played a pivotal role in its storyline.
Enjoy the one-shot performance of this track featuring heartfelt lyrics that portray a withdrawn heart blossoming under the warmth of spring sunshine called friendship, merging with a refreshing and vibrant band sound, exclusively on THE FIRST TAKE.
